I'm hauling right now.

01:26.053 --> 01:29.922
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Darryl and Lisa took on jobs</i>
<i>no one else would touch.</i>

01:29.924 --> 01:32.891
<i>Darrell:</i>
<i>We're definitely walking across</i>
<i>pretty thin ice out here.</i>

01:32.893 --> 01:35.394
Nobody's on this road
for a reason.

01:35.396 --> 01:39.364
Lisa:
This is crazy! Whaa-hoo!

01:41.101 --> 01:43.068
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>But last week,</i>
<i>the new business owners</i>

01:43.070 --> 01:45.270
<i>scored a potential</i>
<i>game changer.</i>

01:45.272 --> 01:46.672
This will put us on the map.

01:46.674 --> 01:52.111
