that road's like.

02:00.187 --> 02:04.690
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Urgently needed to upgrade</i>
<i>the town's energy supply.</i>

02:04.692 --> 02:06.692
<i>Lisa:</i>
<i>If we don't get this convoy</i>
<i>moving</i>

02:06.694 --> 02:09.595
